Took the Antigen Rapid Test (ART) for COVID-19 before attending Parliament this afternoon. It was quick and painless. 

During Phase 3, such testing will become a regular occurrence. This will allow infectious cases to be quickly identified (particularly asymptomatic cases), isolated and treated. Then the community at large can be kept safe, and life and work can continue more normally. ‚Äì LHL

